title: Red & Black Gala Celebrates Best in Tech Athletics - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Red & Black Gala Celebrates Best in Tech Athletics - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: Texas Tech Athletics celebrated its best and brightest from the 2021-22 academic year Sunday evening during the Red and Black Gala hosted by the J.T. and Margaret Talkington Department of Student-Athlete Development at Buddy Holly Hall.
